[src:dpkg/dpkg-deb-1-en] Uniform compression is the default (since dpkg 1.19.0).
[src:dpkg/dpkg-deb-1-en] Sets the maximum number of threads allowed for compressors that support multi-threaded operations (since dpkg 1.21.9).
[src:dpkg/dpkg-deb-1-en] Set the owner and group for each entry in the filesystem tree data to root with id 0 (since dpkg 1.19.0).
